{"tid":304951,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[毒撚出城]淡季北海道遊DAY 1","createTime":"2017-07-01T09:55:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-01T14:15:16.000Z","uid":92698,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d01f290131dc210a7bdfa49c1111b0af81a264d5","tid":304951,"uid":92698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T09:55:42.000Z","msg":"HELLO 大家好！這次是小弟第一次寫遊記，如有不足之處請多多包涵！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n出發日期：2017年5月28日～2017年6月1日 (5天)<br />\n<br />\n是次行程規劃<br />\nDAY 1 ：香港國際機場 (CX580 09:20) -&gt; 北海道新千歲機場(15:30) -&gt; 快速Airport號(16:30)到小樽(17:46) -&gt; 酒店Check-in -&gt; 酒店泡湯 -&gt; 中央通和小樽運河 -&gt; 函太郎迴轉壽司晚飯 -&gt; 休息<br />\n<br />\nDAY 2 ：Central Town都通 -&gt; SUN MALL一番街 -&gt; 壽司通 -&gt; 手宮線遺跡 -&gt; 堺町 -&gt; 小樽浪漫館 -&gt; 小樽大正硝子館 -&gt; 出世前廣場 -&gt; 水芭蕉 -&gt; OTARU家 -&gt; Otaru Poseidon Main Shop 小樽ポセイ丼本店午餐 -&gt; Ika Taro Honpo いか太郎本舗 -&gt; 硝屋 -&gt; 小樽音樂盒堂2號館 -&gt; 蒸氣時鐘 -&gt; Otaru Music Box Museum 小樽音樂盒堂本館 -&gt; 夢之音 -&gt;  LeTAO Head Store 小樽洋菓子舗ルタオ本店 -&gt; Kitakaro Otaru Main Shop 北菓楼小樽本館 -&gt; Rokatei Otaru Canal Shop 六花亭 小樽運河店 -&gt; 小樽市観光物産プラザ（運河プラザ）-&gt; 出抜小路 -&gt; 北とうがらし出抜小路店晚飯 -&gt; 休息<br />\n<br />\nDAY 3 ：三角市場 -&gt; 市場食堂 味処たけだ早餐 -&gt; JR(11:00)回札幌(11:40) -&gt; Sapporo Station Bus Terminal 札幌駅バスターミナル -&gt; 定鐵快速7(12:15)到定山溪(13:15) -&gt; 酒店Check-in -&gt; 二見公園 -&gt; 二見河畔園地(散策步道) -&gt; 河童大王 -&gt; 二見吊橋 -&gt; 河童淵 -&gt; 岩戸観世音(寿と健康の足つぼの湯) -&gt; 定山溪大橋 -&gt; 白糸の滝 -&gt; 足のふれあい太郎の湯 -&gt; 定山溪觀光案內所 -&gt; 北海道三景之碑 -&gt; 月見橋 -&gt; J・glacee（ジェイグラッセ）下午茶 -&gt; 回酒店泡湯 -&gt;酒店自助晚餐 -&gt; 休息<br />\n<br />\nDAY 4 ：酒店自助早餐 -&gt; 酒店專車(10:00)回札幌(11:00) -&gt; 札幌酒店Check-in -&gt; Garaku Soup Curry スープカレーＧＡＲＡＫＵ 午餐 -&gt; DAISO -&gt; 狸小路 -&gt; Tokyu Hands -&gt; 北菓楼 札幌本館 （旧 北海道庁立図書館）-&gt; 大通公園 -&gt; 札幌電視塔 さっぽろテレビ塔 -&gt; BAPE STORE 札幌店 -&gt; 薄野閒逛 -&gt; スープカレーSAMURAI さくら店 晚飯 -&gt; ドン・キホーテ 札幌店掃貨 -&gt; 休息<br />\n<br />\nDAY 5 ：酒店Check-out -&gt; 新善光寺 -&gt; 二条かに市場 -&gt; 丸本本間鮮魚店午飯 -&gt; 能登水產 -&gt; JR去新千歲機場 -&gt; えびそば一幻 新千歳空港店下午茶 -&gt; 回香港<br />\n<br />\n事不宜遲，即刻去片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nDAY 1 (28/5/2017)：香港國際機場 (CX580 09:20) -&gt; 北海道新千歲機場15:30 -&gt; 坐16:30的快速Airport號到小樽17:46到 -&gt; 酒店Check-in -&gt; 酒店泡湯 -&gt; 中央通和小樽運河 -&gt; 函太郎迴轉壽司晚飯 -&gt; 休息<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n小弟很喜歡挑淡季出國旅遊，原因是旅客比較少，無論去景點或是走在大街上也比較舒適自在(極討厭人多擠迫的地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )，還有就是可以感受當地人較親切真誠的對待<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n這次在5月下旬旅行選擇了北海道，將會是我第二次踏足此地(第一次是在去年6月份畢業旅行)。可能你會問：沒有雪沒有櫻花沒有薰衣草，看點在哪啊Hi Auntie<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我不去我不去！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 放心，接下來就讓你感受一下淡季的北海道，原來也可以很好玩！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n因為單獨自助遊的關係，很多計劃都是隨心所欲，時間也容易預算<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 2017年5月28號早上的飛機(CX580 09:20)，可惜遇上延誤10點才起飛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 幸好從香港到北海道只需要4小時的航程(從台灣出發的直航航空有長榮、中華跟Budget Airline，航程約3個半小時左右)，吃過飛機餐看過迪士尼最新電影《美女與野獸》後便抵達北海道了！Emma Watson真的很漂亮～<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (陶醉中)<br />\n<br />\n下飛機的時候大約是3點半，拿行李後便去JR車站坐JR去小樽，可是抵達時剛好miss了4點正發車的JR<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 只好等4點半的班次了(快速AIRPORT號往來新千歲空港及小樽時刻表：<a href=\"http://www2.jrhokkaido.co.jp/global/chinese/ttable/05.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww2.jrhokkaido.co.jp%2Fglobal%2Fchinese%2Fttable%2F05.pdf&d=WsVp9cz2p4TlZYGa46ugDf7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=7082c50d\" target=\"_blank\">http://www2.jrhokkaido.co.jp/global/chinese/ttable/05.pdf</a>)。現在北海道除了KITACA卡之外，用其他IC晶片卡都可以，比如ICOCA卡、SUICA卡。小弟旅費不多，選擇了自由席，知道車程要70分鐘所以一上車就呼呼大睡，一醒來剛好到總站小樽。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91c00b66d795fdf3fe965a5b318fab96aa9aed7a","tid":304951,"uid":92698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T09:58:04.000Z","msg":"提著行李箱來到這次入住的酒店，是天然温泉 灯の湯 ドーミーインPREMIUM小樽 (Dormy Inn Premium Otaru Natural Hot Spring) ，中文是Dormy Inn高階酒店 - 小樽天然溫泉。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n地址：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com.hk/maps/place/Dormy+Inn+Premium+Otaru+Natural+Hot+Spring/@43.198419,140.9925323,17z/data=!3m1!4b1!4m5!3m4!1s0x5f0ae1acd7c98543:0xb6cd3164ddb905b7!8m2!3d43.198419!4d140.994721?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.hk%2Fmaps%2Fplace%2FDormy%2BInn%2BPremium%2BOtaru%2BNatural%2BHot%2BSpring%2F%4043.198419%2C140.9925323%2C17z%2Fdata%3D%213m1%214b1%214m5%213m4%211s0x5f0ae1acd7c98543%3A0xb6cd3164ddb905b7%218m2%213d43.198419%214d140.994721%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=WsVp9cz2p4TlZYGa46ugDf7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=b28994ea\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com.hk/maps/place/Dormy+Inn+Premium+Otaru+Natural+Hot+Spring/@43.198419,140.9925323,17z/data=!3m1!4b1!4m5!3m4!1s0x5f0ae1acd7c98543:0xb6cd3164ddb905b7!8m2!3d43.198419!4d140.994721?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n<br />\n酒店超級好找，就在小樽JR車站門口對面左方當眼處，走路2分鐘就到了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 預訂的是男士膠囊房，只要370港幣住兩個晚上，CP值超高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> Check in後進房間把行李寄放在儲物箱後立即去溫泉爽一下，這裡的溫泉名為灯之湯(詳細介紹：<a href=\"http://www.hotespa.net/hotels/otaru/spa/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hotespa.net%2Fhotels%2Fotaru%2Fspa%2F&d=WsVp9cz2p4TlZYGa46ugDf7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=6e820fa3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.hotespa.net/hotels/otaru/spa/</a>)，室內的兩個溫泉都有點過熱不太喜歡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 去了室外的溫泉跟檜風呂超舒服，大推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/01/175140_f33f43940be70d922f42396cb471289e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F01%2F175140_f33f43940be70d922f42396cb471289e.jpg&h=d0296f7e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/01/175141_3fc1d87ae9551e12b34edda158740a03.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F01%2F175141_3fc1d87ae9551e12b34edda158740a03.jpg&h=5b8d5267&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/01/175142_6911fa333ade1e9729380f27e010ee63.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F01%2F175142_6911fa333ade1e9729380f27e010ee63.jpg&h=4efe5384&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/01/175143_6c08a3a1e44991f91fe701e1cbbaad5b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F01%2F175143_6c08a3a1e44991f91fe701e1cbbaad5b.jpg&h=ac5c699f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/01/175145_2fe98ec2de2c781729b3ad010c7570e5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F01%2F175145_2fe98ec2de2c781729b3ad010c7570e5.jpg&h=137954f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/01/175146_0a9c4ec5c34296498096c47762b49470.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F01%2F175146_0a9c4ec5c34296498096c47762b49470.jpg&h=14709e7b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/01/175148_661c9dc846285ec470476146393edc44.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F01%2F175148_661c9dc846285ec470476146393edc44.jpg&h=7dd71b38&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/01/175149_637ee5dcb5779b780d7de8b07dd13e65.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F01%2F175149_637ee5dcb5779b780d7de8b07dd13e65.jpg&h=f8de95db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n反應好就繼續，多謝支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57a855ba7c837302c6bb3110f04e37f5bc8baf2f","tid":304951,"uid":38591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T10:39:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"55ca3b6d54126d9a7f760cfd156f7cab4d942897","tid":304951,"uid":92698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T11:15:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>推</blockquote><br />\n多謝支持"},{"pid":"21ec881751bec6231e3d62876a6efe17d5464cb0","tid":304951,"uid":33727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T11:52:10.000Z","msg":"每一日遊記開一個post? <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc982f2c1a0619aae64dd156d99b1773b3f2f62c","tid":304951,"uid":92698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T13:02:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>每一日遊記開一個post? <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係，我想睇反應，分開post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69c5004ab3894c50a0146f456a762f0861af8651","tid":304951,"uid":92698,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T14:15:16.000Z","msg":"SOR9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 新POST在此<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/305287/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/305287/page/1</a>"}]}